1. kubectl get pods
2. kubens
3. kubectl run --image=nginx:1.26.0 created-the-wrong-way
4. kubectl apply -n namespace-files -f pod.nginx-minimal.yaml
5. kubectl port-foward -n namespace-files -f nginx-minimal 8080:80
6. kubectl apply -f pod.nginx-better.yaml
7. kubectl port-forward nginx-better 8080:8080

Deleting the namespace recursively deletes the resources inside of it!
8. kubectl delete -f namespace.yaml